documentation:
Writes config data to the rstuf config file. The expected data
is a dict of type:

{

    "CURRENT_REPOSITORY": "<repository_name>",

    "REPOSITORIES": {

        "<repository_name>": {

            "artifact_base_url": "<url>",

            "hash_prefix": "<True/False>",

            "metadata_url": "<url>",

            "trusted_root": "<base64_path_string",

        },

    },

    "SERVER": "<server_url>",

}
